B%93ng-Qu%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1-Thang-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-linh-t%C6%B0u-t%C3%A1c/poem-ZFALwW-Oh0NxiQJY2bUNPQ">Phụng đồng Quách cấp sự “Thang đông linh tưu tác” - 奉同郭給事湯東靈湫作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-hi%E1%BA%BFn-n%E1%BA%A1p-s%E1%BB%A9-kh%E1%BB%9Fi-c%C6%B0-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n/poem-f0xgmiJcw9MpYblRLTxDMw">Tặng hiến nạp sứ khởi cư Điền xá nhân - 贈獻納使起居田舍人澄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-T%C3%ADn-thu-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-VwvQemeJwpGd6rHhEcGfPA">Trường Tín thu từ kỳ 2 - 長信秋詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/author-Q_JpPOHTIyzNkB76eQk-WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Qu%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-4G7ag4S5-0veHb5RWtGkeQ">Xuân vịnh - 春詠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Qu%C3%A2n/author-WIhCtLwouoSDlIo0qbk1DA">Ngô Quân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
